HEADWORD: Parelle
<hw>Pa`relle</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>parelle</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A name
for two kinds of dock (<spn>Rumex Patientia</spn> and <spn>Rumex
Hydrolapathum</spn>).</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A kind of lichen
(<spn>Lecanora parella</spn>) once used in dyeing and in the preparation
of litmus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

